titles.title: A bill to make a technical correction with respect to the temporary duty suspension for clomiphene citrate.

action.text: Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR S13286)
Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 10/7/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tarif Schedule of the United States to make a technical correction to the Schedule with respect to the temporary duty suspension for clomiphene citrate.
